    "The authors utilized selective masking (assisted by attention mapping) to keep track of the identified entities and certain keywords that are relevantly contextually supplementary information or cues about the listed entities in the input phrase.",
    "The innovative text reconstruction or denoising job that ACLM is optimized for is based on BART.",
    "Furthermore, they showed that ACLM may be used in other fields (like biomedicine) when data is scarce.",
    "Jimmy et al. [98] demonstrated NER model for Manipuri that incorporates an embedding method with a BiLSTM deep neural network in which the embedding method includes word embedding along with a character-level word representation from BiLSTM [85] in order to act as a characteristic for the Bi-LSTM NER model.",
    "The author suggested a model to capture the relationship between the output tags by using a CRF classifier."
